headline: Assessing J. M. Smucker (SJM) Valuation As Shares Trade Near Recent Levels
summary: J. M. Smucker (SJM) has drawn fresh attention after recent trading left the share price at US$101.61, with returns roughly flat over the past month and slightly negative across the past 3 months. See our latest analysis for J. M. Smucker. That pickup in recent trading comes after a 5.94% 7 day share price return and a year to date share price return of 5.15%, while the 3 year total shareholder return of 27.27% and 5 year total shareholder return of 3.65% point to much more muted longer term...
